{"id": "art-391", "label": "Art. 391", "title": "Art. 391: Stabilirea numărului total de funcţii publice de conducere în cadrul fiecărei autorităţi sau instituţii publice", "slug": "art-391", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 391: Stabilirea num&#259;rului total de func&#355;ii publice de\nconducere în cadrul fiec&#259;rei autorit&#259;&#355;i sau institu&#355;ii\npublice </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1960768805\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1342\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1960768805\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Num&#259;rul total al func&#355;iilor publice de\nconducere din cadrul autorit&#259;&#355;ii sau institu&#355;iei publice, cu\nexcep&#355;ia func&#355;iilor publice de secretar general al\nunit&#259;&#355;ii/subdiviziunii administrativ-teritoriale, precum &#351;i al\nfunc&#355;iilor publice de conducere a c&#259;ror ocupare se face prin\ndeta&#351;are cu personal din cadrul institu&#355;iilor din sectorul de\nap&#259;rare, ordine public&#259; &#351;i siguran&#355;&#259;\nna&#355;ional&#259;, conform statelor de organizare aprobate, în\ncondi&#355;iile legii, este de maximum 8% din num&#259;rul total al posturilor\naprobate la nivel de ordonator principal de credite.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1108278890\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1341\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1108278890\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Pentru\ndeterminarea num&#259;rului total al func&#355;iilor de conducere prin\naplicarea cotei de 8% prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) se procedeaz&#259; dup&#259;\ncum urmeaz&#259;:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_300253939\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1340\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_300253939\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)în cazul în care num&#259;rul rezultat este mai mic de\nunu, acesta se rotunje&#351;te la întreg;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1826649870\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1339\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1826649870\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)în cazul în care num&#259;rul rezultat este mai mare de\nunu, acesta se rotunje&#351;te la num&#259;rul întreg imediat superior\nacestuia, dac&#259; frac&#355;iunea este mai mare sau egal&#259; cu 0,50.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1838154370\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1338\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1838154370\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Structura\norganizatoric&#259; a autorit&#259;&#355;ilor &#351;i institu&#355;iilor\npublice trebuie s&#259; respecte urm&#259;toarele cerin&#355;e:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_559049567\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1337\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_559049567\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)pentru constituirea unui serviciu este necesar un\nnum&#259;r de minimum 10 posturi de execu&#355;ie;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1883758804\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1336\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1883758804\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)pentru constituirea unei direc&#355;ii este necesar un\nnum&#259;r de minimum 20 de posturi de execu&#355;ie;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1701870478\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1335\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1701870478\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)pentru constituirea unei direc&#355;ii generale este\nnecesar un num&#259;r de minimum 35 de posturi de execu&#355;ie.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}